</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-geographical-scope field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Geographical Scope:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_geographical_scope%3A175">National</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-purpose field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Purpose</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-influence-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">What was the intended purpose?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_influence_kind%3A22">Consultation (i.e. to advise decision makers)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_influence_kind%3A27">Raise public awareness</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_influence_kind%3A52">Develop individual capacities (e.g. skills, learning)</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-history field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">History</span></h3>
